      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;why-am-i-creating-this-post&#34;&gt;Why am I creating this post?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I felt that it will be a way to jot down my experiences while creating this blog, this will allow me to share my thoughts. After  &amp;lsquo;googling&amp;rsquo;, it was not as intimidating as I thought. I was surprised that it was simpler than I thought.&lt;/p&gt;
