&lt;p&gt;Git&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There are basics git commands that we need to know, learn more from &lt;a href=&#34;https://towardsdatascience.com/10-git-commands-that-will-get-you-started-right-now-94d814761919&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
